Source: thailatex
Section: tex
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Chanop Silpa-Anan <chanop@debian.org>
Build-Depends-Indep: debhelper (>=4.0.0), tetex-bin (>=2.0.2), gs, gs-common
Standards-Version: 3.5.8

Package: thailatex
Architecture: all 
Recommends: cttex|swath
Depends: tetex-bin (>=2.0.2), tetex-base (>=2.0.2)
Description: Thai Latex package
 This package provides Thai language add-on for Latex. It is based on 
 babel package which comes with tetex distribution.
 .
 This package needs Thai words separator such as cttex and swath, in
 order for latex to be able to break sentences.
